<h2 style="color:#18181b; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 16px;">Reset your password</h2>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  Hey <%= @resource.first_name.presence || @resource.username.presence || "there" %> —
</p>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  We received a request to reset the password for your Train Like Dubi account (<strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>).
  Click the button below to choose a new password.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center; margin:0 0 28px;">
  <%= link_to "Reset Password",
      edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token),
      style: "display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; background-color:#dc2626; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;" %>
</p>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7; margin:0 0 20px;">

<p style="color:#71717a; font-size:13px; margin:0 0 8px;">
  This link expires in 6 hours. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password won't change.
</p>

<p style="color:#71717a; font-size:13px; margin:0;">
  If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
  <span style="word-break:break-all; color:#a1a1aa;"><%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></span>
</p>
